OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe hot sunshine to end the day, though
OL,7,Fa few heavy and possibly thundery
OL,8,Fshowers could break out, with further
OL,9,Fshowers developing from the southwest
OL,10,Fovernight. Towards dawn it should turn
OL,11,Fdrier and clearer. Very mild, though
OL,12,Fbreezy.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FThe morning will be dry with
OL,15,Fplenty of very warm or hot sunshine.
OL,16,FSome cloud developing heading into the
OL,17,Fafternoon, giving a risk of a heavy,
OL,18,Fpossibly thundery shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
